== Space-based observatories == * [[Chandra X-ray Observatory]] * [[Hinode]] * [[Kepler mission|Kepler]] * [[Solar Dynamics Observatory|Solar Dynamics Observatory (SDO)]] * [[SOHO spacecraft|Solar and Heliospheric Observatory (SOHO)]] * [[Spitzer Space Telescope]]
