The Center receives 70% of its funding from [[NASA]], 22% from [[Smithsonian Institution|Smithsonian]] federal funds and 4% from the [[National Science Foundation]]. The remaining 4% comes from contributors including the [[United States Department of Energy]], the [[Annenberg Foundation]], and gifts and endowments.{{fact|date=March 2018}}
